name: Ameyaw Nancy
description: Talking about my self, I love friends and family, I am a fun person and make friends easily. I love life, love my family and still have some love to share with a special man. Life can be lonely without someone…I am a person who is very real when it comes to life and its’ issues. Am honest, kind caring, affectionate, good sense of humor, easy going, free thinker, trustworthy and respect the lives of other. looking for someone who will understand me as I am.
